headline: Synopsys (NasdaqGS:SNPS) Surges 41% Over Last Quarter
summary: Synopsys (NasdaqGS:SNPS) recently saw a significant share price increase of 41% over the last quarter, likely influenced by several key developments. The company's addition to multiple Russell indices, such as the Russell 1000 and 3000 Value Benchmarks, may have bolstered investor confidence, reflecting its strengthened market position. Additionally, strategic collaborations with Broadcom and Keysight Technologies showcased its commitment to enhancing AI infrastructures and RF design...
